267
00:22:18,880 --> 00:22:19,720
Hey.

268
00:22:20,640 --> 00:22:24,160
That's not true. Why would you think that?

269
00:22:25,880 --> 00:22:27,840
But if everyone feels uncomfortable,

270
00:22:29,160 --> 00:22:30,560
I will redo it.

271
00:22:30,640 --> 00:22:31,480
CHEATER

272
00:22:31,560 --> 00:22:33,320
<i>And to apologize…</i>

273
00:22:33,400 --> 00:22:34,640
REDO IT

274
00:22:34,720 --> 00:22:36,120
<i>…it won't just be a date anymore.</i>

275
00:22:36,200 --> 00:22:37,080
YES, THAT WAS CHEATING

276
00:22:37,760 --> 00:22:40,200
It will be a one-night stand with me.

277
00:22:44,720 --> 00:22:48,160
<i>Whoever donates the most</i>
<i>to the education fund will get it.</i>

278
00:22:50,520 --> 00:22:52,600
No more drawing lots.

279
00:22:53,560 --> 00:22:55,880
In three days, I will announce the winner.

280
00:22:56,480 --> 00:22:58,680
<i>Please donate a lot.</i>

281
00:23:07,800 --> 00:23:09,640
BALANCE: 0.75 BAHT

282
00:23:25,560 --> 00:23:26,840
Expel her, Teacher.

283
00:23:27,880 --> 00:23:29,560
I think Nanno has gone too far.

284
00:23:30,920 --> 00:23:33,120
Oh? So our bodies
don't belong to us anymore?

285
00:23:34,800 --> 00:23:36,160
They do.

286
00:23:36,240 --> 00:23:38,320
But this counts as prostitution.

287
00:23:38,400 --> 00:23:41,040
- It's illegal, Teacher.
- No.

288
00:23:41,120 --> 00:23:43,040
If both sides consent,

289
00:23:43,120 --> 00:23:44,560
then it's called consent.

290
00:23:45,400 --> 00:23:48,040
And besides,
Nanno is doing it for charity.

291
00:23:48,560 --> 00:23:50,800
I think you're being too conservative.

292
00:24:04,600 --> 00:24:11,240
JOIN THE EDUCATION FUND DONATION.
TOP DONATOR GETS A NIGHT WITH NANNO.

293
00:24:20,920 --> 00:24:23,120
Hey, come here.

294
00:24:23,200 --> 00:24:24,400
Did you donate?

295
00:24:24,920 --> 00:24:26,440
For Nanno. She's live now.

296
00:24:26,520 --> 00:24:28,120
- Open it now.
- Really?

297
00:24:33,240 --> 00:24:35,120
Suea, why did you go into my room?

298
00:24:35,760 --> 00:24:37,560
Are you going to eat or not?

299
00:24:39,400 --> 00:24:41,240
THE RESULT WILL BE ANNOUNCED IN TWO DAYS

300
00:24:48,800 --> 00:24:50,920
THE RESULT WILL BE ANNOUNCED TOMORROW

301
00:25:05,120 --> 00:25:07,640
TRANSFER COMPLETE
100,000 BAHT

302
00:25:35,800 --> 00:25:37,160
Suea, aren't you going to school?

303
00:25:38,560 --> 00:25:40,080
Yeah, Mom. I'll go soon.

304
00:25:40,160 --> 00:25:41,320
I'M SO EXCITED

305
00:25:41,400 --> 00:25:42,640
I CAN'T WAIT

306
00:25:42,720 --> 00:25:45,120
At this moment,
I would like to take this opportunity

307
00:25:45,200 --> 00:25:50,280
to allow Nanno to use this stage
to declare her bodily freedom.

308
00:25:56,840 --> 00:26:00,400
Thank you to everyone
who made today possible.

309
00:26:01,240 --> 00:26:05,000
I can't believe that my body

310
00:26:05,520 --> 00:26:08,400
could create so many miracles.

311
00:26:10,240 --> 00:26:12,360
But for me to get here today,

312
00:26:13,080 --> 00:26:15,440
there is one person
I must thank above all.

313
00:26:16,600 --> 00:26:18,240
And that person is

314
00:26:18,320 --> 00:26:19,440
Blossom.

315
00:26:25,800 --> 00:26:28,480
If Blossom hadn't inspired me

316
00:26:29,000 --> 00:26:33,440
and said that
our bodies should belong to us,

317
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:36,640
we probably wouldn't be having
this much fun today.

318
00:26:38,640 --> 00:26:40,720
Thank you very much, Blossom.

319
00:26:48,600 --> 00:26:51,960
All right, let's find out

320
00:26:52,480 --> 00:26:54,520
who donated the most

321
00:26:55,080 --> 00:26:57,280
and will receive

322
00:26:58,200 --> 00:27:00,320
a one-night stand with me.

323
00:27:03,160 --> 00:27:05,360
I won't announce their name.

324
00:27:05,880 --> 00:27:09,240
Instead, I will announce the number.

325
00:27:12,640 --> 00:27:14,560
<i>And the number</i>

326
00:27:15,800 --> 00:27:17,320
is…

327
00:27:20,440 --> 00:27:21,600
one…

328
00:27:27,880 --> 00:27:29,360
zero…

329
00:27:33,200 --> 00:27:34,160
nine.

330
00:27:37,560 --> 00:27:38,720
Damn it!

331
00:27:40,280 --> 00:27:42,560
Number 109.

332
00:27:42,640 --> 00:27:46,240
Meet me at The Royal Resort Park Hotel,

333
00:27:47,280 --> 00:27:50,760
room 205.

334
00:27:52,280 --> 00:27:53,760
At 8:00 p.m.

335
00:27:56,880 --> 00:27:58,760
See you there.

336
00:27:58,840 --> 00:28:00,200
I'll be waiting.

337
00:28:08,720 --> 00:28:10,400
WHO'S 109?

338
00:28:10,480 --> 00:28:11,880
NOT ME

339
00:28:12,680 --> 00:28:15,200
Did she cheat again?

340
00:28:15,280 --> 00:28:17,080
WITH THIS MUCH MONEY,
OF COURSE I WOULDN'T WIN

341
00:28:17,160 --> 00:28:18,840
WHO THE HELL IS HE? HE'S LOADED.

342
00:28:34,120 --> 00:28:39,520
109 GETTING HER ALL TO HIMSELF ISN'T FAIR.
EVERYONE SHOULD GET SOMETHING.

343
00:28:47,640 --> 00:28:48,760
TRUE. WE ALSO DONATED A LOT.

344
00:28:48,840 --> 00:28:50,880
BITCH. GIVE ME MY MONEY BACK.

345
00:28:57,080 --> 00:28:58,000
Where are you going?

346
00:28:58,080 --> 00:28:59,280
You can't go in!

347
00:28:59,360 --> 00:29:02,240
- You can't go in!
- Wait!

348
00:29:02,320 --> 00:29:05,000
- If you're not a guest, you can't go in.
- We are the guests.

349
00:29:05,080 --> 00:29:06,480
Room 205.

350
00:29:06,560 --> 00:29:08,280
- Yeah, that's right.
- Yeah.

351
00:29:08,360 --> 00:29:10,800
- There are too many of you.
- I told you we're the guests.

352
00:29:26,000 --> 00:29:29,240
Damn it. Number 109,
you can't keep Nanno all to yourself.

353
00:29:29,320 --> 00:29:31,360
Damn it. Let me see your face.

354
00:29:31,880 --> 00:29:33,280
- What the hell?
- Shit.

355
00:29:43,840 --> 00:29:46,880
<i>The person who donated the most</i>
<i>to the education fund</i>

356
00:29:48,480 --> 00:29:52,160
<i>will get a one-night stand with me.</i>

357
00:29:53,040 --> 00:29:55,240
274,600 BAHT
CONFIRM TRANSACTION

358
00:29:58,640 --> 00:30:00,800
Number 109.

359
00:30:04,800 --> 00:30:06,680
You used your money
to do something like this?

360
00:30:06,760 --> 00:30:07,880
Get down here!

361
00:30:07,960 --> 00:30:10,000
Drag him down! Beat him up!

362
00:30:18,480 --> 00:30:21,560
Calm down. What's going on here?

363
00:30:23,480 --> 00:30:25,120
She's telling us to calm down.

364
00:30:28,120 --> 00:30:30,200
How the hell are we supposed to stay calm?

365
00:30:30,720 --> 00:30:33,160
We spent so much money on you.

366
00:30:33,760 --> 00:30:35,520
And we didn't get anything at all.

367
00:30:36,400 --> 00:30:38,640
But everything went
according to the rules.

368
00:30:39,160 --> 00:30:40,960
What rules?

369
00:30:43,000 --> 00:30:46,480
Me and the OnlyNanno fans,

370
00:30:47,000 --> 00:30:48,440
we paid you so much money.

371
00:30:48,520 --> 00:30:52,280
But that old bastard lying over there
gets you all to himself.

372
00:30:52,880 --> 00:30:54,320
That's not fair.

373
00:30:55,360 --> 00:30:57,160
Your body,

374
00:30:58,200 --> 00:30:59,680
everything that belongs to you,

375
00:30:59,760 --> 00:31:01,440
should belong to us too.

376
00:31:01,520 --> 00:31:02,600
Oh?

377
00:31:03,480 --> 00:31:05,440
Didn't everyone support the idea that

378
00:31:05,960 --> 00:31:10,400
my body belongs to me?

379
00:31:14,760 --> 00:31:16,160
It's your body,

380
00:31:17,440 --> 00:31:19,080
but it's my money.

381
00:31:28,200 --> 00:31:30,320
Then what should we do to make it fair?

382
00:31:33,120 --> 00:31:35,920
Should I divide myself
into pieces for everyone?

383
00:31:40,200 --> 00:31:41,520
Then come and take it.

384
00:32:03,840 --> 00:32:07,400
My body, my choice, Blossom.

385
00:32:40,720 --> 00:32:42,880
Welcome back to my channel.

386
00:32:45,880 --> 00:32:47,400
Just like I said,

387
00:32:50,680 --> 00:32:54,920
our bodies belong to us.

388
00:32:57,640 --> 00:32:58,720
So…

389
00:34:02,400 --> 00:34:05,040
<i>We have to stop the opening</i>
<i>of the Hundred-Year Building.</i>

390
00:34:05,760 --> 00:34:08,200
<i>Your group wants to expose</i>
<i>the building corruption, right?</i>

391
00:34:08,280 --> 00:34:09,560
<i>I'll help you.</i>

392
00:34:12,200 --> 00:34:14,600
<i>Nanno, whose side are you really on? </i>

393
00:34:16,480 --> 00:34:19,000
Don't disappoint me.

394
00:34:20,560 --> 00:34:21,720
Shit.

395
00:34:26,080 --> 00:34:28,800
<i>If the Exclamation group</i>
<i>releases this clip,</i>

396
00:34:28,880 --> 00:34:30,880
<i>they're dead.</i>

397
00:34:33,760 --> 00:34:35,440
The Exclamation group
still hasn't given up?

398
00:34:36,040 --> 00:34:37,360
<i>Hide the truth.</i>

399
00:34:38,680 --> 00:34:40,440
- Shit.
<i>- Distract.</i>

400
00:34:41,440 --> 00:34:43,960
<i>That's the art</i>
<i>of those who control the game.</i>

401
00:34:44,040 --> 00:34:45,240
Checkmate.

402
00:34:47,800 --> 00:34:49,640
This time,
they're definitely going to die.

403
00:36:44,360 --> 00:36:49,360
Subtitle translation by: Panuwat Baikeawon
